Program: Great Lives
Title: Henri Matisse
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b007646h
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 3 Jan 2020
Writer Frank Delaney and biographer Hilary Spurling discuss the painter Henri Matisse. With Humphrey Carpenter. From 2001. The biographical series in which a distinguished guest chooses someone who's inspired their life. Will their hero stand up to intensive scrutiny and merit the description of having led a great life? Show less